BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:xLEks-Yv9i5cl-D7bMjcj
SUMMARY:Dr. Bertha Hidalgo
DTSTAMP:20260326T121833Z
DTSTART:20260407T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Dr. Bertha Hidalgo as she explores how epigenetics is resh
	aping our understanding of hypertensive pregnancy disorders. This lecture 
	highlights population-based insights\\\, early biomarkers of risk\\\, and 
	transformative strategies for prevention—advancing maternal health equity 
	and innovation in public health.\n\nhttps://townhallseattle.org/event/dr-b
	ertha-hidalgo/\n\nFrom Town Hall Seattle
